ds * [[Martin Handford]], ''[[Where's Wally?]]'' * [[Steven Harris (cartoonist)|Steven Harris]] * [[Andrew Kennaway Henderson]] * [[Henfil]], Brazilian cartoonist * [[Hergé]], ''[[The Adventures of Tintin]]'' * [[George Herriman]], ''[[Krazy Kat]]'' * [[Watson Heston]] * [[Stephen Hillenburg]], ''[[SpongeBob SquarePants]]'' * [[Bill Hinds]], "Tank McNamara" * [[Dick Hodgins, Jr.]] * [[William Hogarth]], English pictorial satirist and editorial cartoonist; credited with pioneering western [[sequential art]]; work ranged from [[Realism (visual arts)|realistic]] portraiture to [[comic strip]] * [[Bill Holbrook]], ''[[On the Fastrack]]'', ''[[Safe Havens]]'', and ''[[Kevin and Kell]]'' * [[Nicole Hollander]], ''[[Sylvia (comic strip)|Sylvia]]'' * [[John Holmstrom]] * [[Geoff "Jeff" Hook]], Australian * [[George William Houghton]], British golf cartoonist * [[Jim Hummel]] * [[Edgar Pierre Jacobs]], ''[[Blake and Mortimer]]'' * [[Al Jaffee]], ''[[Mad (magazine)|Mad]]'' * [[Kirk Jarvinen]] * [[S. Jithesh]], World's Fastest Performing Cartoonist * [[Herbert Johnson (cartoonist)|Herbert Johnson]] * [[Mike Judge]], ''[[Beavis and Butt-head]]'', ''[[King of the Hill]]'', ''[[The Goode Family]]'' * [[Arja Kajermo]] * [[Avi Katz (illustrator)|Avi Katz]] * [[Bil Keane]], "Family Circus" * [[Jeff Keane]]. "Family Circus" * [[Walt Kelly]], ''[[Pogo (comics)|Pogo]]'' * [[Rik Kemp]] * [[Molly Kiely]] * [[Wyncie King]] * [[Jeff Kinney (writer)|Jeff Kinney]], ''[[Diary of a Wimpy Kid]]'' * [[Rick Kirkman]], "Baby Blues" * [[Heinrich Kley]] * [[B. Kliban]] * [[John Kricfalusi]], ''[[The Ren & Stimpy Show]]'' * [[Gary Larson]], ''[[The Far Side]]'' * [[Rick Law]], ''[[Beyond the Veil (comics)|Beyond the Veil]]'' * [[R K Laxman]], cartoonist for ''[[The Times of India]]'', [[India]] * [[Mell Lazarus]]. "[[Momma]], [[Miss Peach]]" * [[John Leech (caricaturist)|John Leech]], 19th-century ''Punch'' cartoonist * [[Michael Leunig]], Australian * [[Arnold Levin]] * [[David Liljemark]] * [[Neil 